    "question": "What is the path from the TMT Projet root to the Pupil Alignmnet Error Budget analysis?",
    "durationMs": 316973,
    "status": "OK",
    "finalAnswer": "The path from the TMT Project root to the Pupil Alignment Error Budget analysis is:\n\n**TMT → Project → Work Packages → Telescope → Work Packages → Control → Alignment and Phasing System → Systems Engineering → 10 Analysis → Roll-up Analyses → Error Budgets → Pupil Alignment Error Budget**\n\nThis is a package hierarchy under the TMT::Project::Work Packages::Telescope::Work Packages::Control::Alignment and Phasing System::Systems Engineering::10 Analysis::Roll-up Analyses::Error Budgets namespace.\n\nThe \"Pupil Alignment Error Budget\" is a package (type: vocab:package) that contains error budget analysis elements including:\n- Knowledge of APT-TMT interface point\n- Error between Reference Point and fiducials\n- Alignment of M3 to APS-TMT interface point\n- Error in global alignment of APS using fiducials\n- Stimulus Pupil Shift Error\n- Knowledge of the Shear Plate angle\n- And other error budget components",
    "error": null,
